column2: SELECT TOP # fld.run, fld.avg_sky_muJy, fld.runarea AS area, IS# (fp.nfirstmatch, #) FROM (SELECT run, sum (primaryArea) AS runarea, #e6*avg (power (cast (#. as float) , #*sky_r) ) as avg_sky_muJy FROM Field GROUP BY run) AS fld LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT p.run, count (*) AS nfirstmatch FROM FIRST AS fm INNER JOIN photoprimary as p ON p.objid = fm.objid GROUP BY p.run) AS fp ON fld.run = fp.run ORDER BY fld.run
